de.oaam.model.oaam.anatomy

Interface Position3D

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Position3DImpl

    public interface Position3D
extends OaamBaseElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Position3 D'. A physical 3D coordinate

    The following features are supported:

    • X
    • Y
    • Z
    See Also:
    AnatomyPackage.getPosition3D()
